Tim Cook, I have a Mac obsession
text:
In 2022, I purchased three M1 machines; two Macbook Pro M1 Pros, and a M1 Studio Max.

I've also invested more than 4 months salary into Apple and I am proud of it.

My primary use case is software development and experimentation (mostly in the realm of WebRTC high-fidelity audio streaming between peers on ad-hoc networks we set up).

The M1 Studio is colocated in Wisconsin and I am in Nicaragua. I've rented various Macs from macminivault.com over the past 2.5 years and decided it would be more economical to just buy a new Studio and ship it to them.

Absolute phenomenal experience.

I'd be interested in hearing if anyone else has this Mac obsession like I do, or perhaps I'm just crazy.

I could care less about any of their other technology. Just the Macs, but I love Apple Music as well.
